caption:
SWIPE ➡️ Raphinha (before the match): “Argentina? We’ll beat them up... Absolutely! Beat them up! On the pitch and off the pitch if we have to!” 🇧🇷

“I’m going to (score a goal against Argentina). I’m going in with everything I’ve got.. F*** THEM!”

And after the match, Argentina players joined the fans who were chanting..

🗣️ “A minute of silence... Shh!... For Raphinha, who is d**d!” 💀
